Text.val: Alleen orders met nog te fiatteren uitvoeringen
// Niet voor de union met ordersdetaillering

ExpSyntax.val: Trim({0,41}) & ' ' &' and ' &IF({0,60}=0,'not exists ','exists ') & '(select d.ord_ordernummer, d.ord_orderregel from orders d, orderlink l, od_verz_order_verwerking s where o.ord_ordernummer = d.ord_ordernummer and o.ord_orderregel = d.ord_orderregel and (d.ord_status <= 2 and (d.ord_ordernummer = s.ovov_ordernummer or d.ord_ordernummer = l.ol_ordernummer_doel and l.ol_ordernummer_bron = s.ovov_ordernummer)))'

'insert into tmp_orders t (t.ort_ordernummer, t.ort_orderregel) ( select distinct o.ord_ordernummer, o.ord_orderregel from orders o' & IF(NOT({0,43}), ', clienten c', '') & IF({0,2}=3, ', clientgroep_view v', '') & ' ' & Trim({0,39})

' union select distinct d.orx_ordernummer, d.orx_orderregel from ordersdetaillering d, orders o where o.ord_ordernummer = d.orx_ordernummer and o.ord_orderregel = d.orx_orderregel ' & Trim({0,40}) & ' ' & Trim({0,41})
' and ' & Trim({0,50}) & ' between ' & Trim({0,51}) & ' and ' & Trim({0,52})
Left({0,38},4) = ' and ' OR (InStr({0,38}, ' and ')>0 AND (InStr({0,38}, ' and ')<InStr({0,38}, ' where ') OR InStr({0,38}, ' where ')=0) )
